commentable_entity.ask: Get Amber Heard removed from Aquaman 2 !!!!!!
commentable_entity.title: DC Comics: Get Amber Heard removed from Aquaman 2 !!!!!!
commentable_entity.description: Its unfair and unjust to allow Amber Heard to continue filming with DC to create the sequel to Aquaman. If Johnny Depp should have to step away from filming Fantastic Beasts 3, then the same should be done for Amber Heard being in Aquaman 2. There is proof of Ms. Heard abusing Mr. Depp even though she claimed he was the one abusing her. Although Johnny Depp is getting money (8 figures) to not be apart of Fantastic Beasts 3, it's the principle of fairness. The people want and have signed signatures for Johnny to be apart of Fantastic Beasts 3 again. Let's all come together and petition again so this time we can get to remove Amber Heard from the movie Aquaman 2.
commentable_entity.letter_body: Get Amber Heard removed from Aquaman 2 !!!!!!
